程序包 it.polimi.ingsw.xyl.model.cosplayer

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    Apollo  
    ApolloMoveTest
    it's a test of cosplayer moving(Apollo) Apollo's move: worker may move into an opponent worker's space by forcing their worker to the space to the space yours just vacated.
    Artemis  
    ArtemisMoveTest
    it's a test of cosplayer moving(Artemis) Artemis' move: worker may move one additional time, but not back to its initial space.
    Athena
    This class represents the role of the Player: Athena Athena's power: if one of your workers moved up on your last turn, opponent workers cannot move up this turn.
    AthenaPowerTest
    it's a test of Athena godpower Athena's power: if one of your workers moved up on your last turn, opponent workers cannot move up this turn.
    AthenaSetOpponentPlayersNoMoveUpTest
    it's a test of Athena godpower interacts with Prometheus and Apollo.
    Atlas  
    AtlasBuildTest
    it's a test of cosplayer building(Atlas) Atlas' build: worker may build a dome at any level.
    Demeter  
    DemeterBuildTest
    it's a test of cosplayer building(Demeter) Demeter's build: worker may build one additional time, but not on the same space.
    GodCosplayerTest
    it's a general test config of God Cosplayer
    Hephaestus  
    HephaestusBuildTest
    it's a test of cosplayer building(Hephaestus) Hephaestus' build: worker may build one additional block(not dome) on top of your first block.
    Minotaur  
    MinotaurMoveTest
    it's a test of cosplayer moving(Minotaur) Minotaur's move: worker may move into an opponent worker's space, if their worker can be forced one space straight backwards to an unoccupied space at ANY level.
    Pan  
    PanWinTest
    it's a test of Pan's Win condition Pan will win if the worker moves down two or more levels
    Prometheus
    This class represents the role of the Player: Prometheus Prometheus' move and build: If your worker does not move up(means to a higher level), it may build both before and after moving.
    PrometheusMoveBuildTest
    it's a test of cosplayer moving and building (Prometheus) Prometheus' move and build: If your worker does not move up(means to a higher level), it may build both before and after moving.
